text: Harald Ekwall (14 December 1873 - 1935) was a Chilean sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1873 births Category:1935 deaths Category:Chilean male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Chile Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Leipzig Category:German emigrants to Chile
